{"id":238,"date":"2019-07-22T14:53:08","date_gmt":"2019-07-22T07:53:08","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.acclime.com\/?page_id=238"},"modified":"2023-10-02T10:20:41","modified_gmt":"2023-10-02T02:20:41","slug":"about","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.acclime.com\/about\/","title":{"rendered":"About us"},"content":{"rendered":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/singapore.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/acclime_web_image_46.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/acclime_web_image_14.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/my-petronas-top.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/singapore.acclime.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/dot-teal.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/acclime_web_image_45.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/acclime-hongkong.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/acclime-vietnam.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/ind-acclime-country-image1.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/dot.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h5><span class=\"acc-orange\">About us<\/span><\/h5>\n<h1>Asia&#8217;s corporate specialist with global standards<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h1>\n<ul>\n<li>\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/www.acclime.com\/download\/2608\/\">Download brochure<\/a>\n    <\/li>\n<li>\n        <a href=\"#more\">Learn more<\/a>\n    <\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>From Asia, for\u00a0Asia<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h2>\n<div>\n<p>Acclime is an Asia-focused corporate services specialist trusted to deliver with speed, flexibility and\u00a0precision.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div>\n<p>We have a genuine, on-the-ground presence in all of Asia\u2019s hardest-to-navigate markets. By staying on top of regulatory changes, we help our clients manage local governmental and administrative compliance issues quickly, with a minimum of fuss.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p>\n    <a href=\"\/locations\/\">View all locations<\/a>\n<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n        <a href=\"\/download\/2608\/\">Download brochure<\/a>\n    <\/li>\n<li>\n        <a href=\"\/download\/6713\/\">\u4f01\u4e1a\u624b\u518c<\/a>\n    <\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/location-map-Acclime.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.acclime.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/countries.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3>Countries in Asia<\/h3>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.acclime.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/global-centres.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3>Global client centres<\/h3>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.acclime.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/active-clients.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3>Active clients<\/h3>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.acclime.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/employees.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3>Employees<\/h3>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3>Acclime companies<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h3>\n<div>\n<p>Companies acquired by Acclime but currently continuing to operate as independent business units.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.fiducia-china.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/fiducia.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/a><br \/>\n<a href=\"https:\/\/www.ocra.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/ocra.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/a><\/p>\n<h6><span class=\"uk-icon uk-icon-image dot-alignment\" style=\"background-image: url(\/wp-content\/uploads\/dot.svg);\"><\/span> Vision &amp; mission<\/h6>\n<h2>Elevating the standards of&nbsp;corporate governance in&nbsp;Asia<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h2>\n<div>\n<p class=\"uk-margin-remove-bottom\">At Acclime, we aspire to become Asia\u2019s premier corporate services firm, elevating the standards of corporate governance everywhere we operate.<\/p>\n<p class=\"uk-margin-remove-bottom\">We are active in all Asian markets, with a particular focus on emerging Asia, where it is difficult to find corporate services firms offering the same high standards and responsiveness as it is in the more mainstream locations such as Hong Kong and Singapore.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<hr>\n<h6><span class=\"uk-icon uk-icon-image dot-alignment\" style=\"background-image: url(\/wp-content\/uploads\/dot.svg);\"><\/span> The Acclime difference<\/h6>\n<h2>Built from the bottom up<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h2>\n<div>\n<p class=\"uk-margin-remove-bottom\">We are unique in the field of corporate services in Asia in that Acclime is partner-owned and its partners are the largest shareholders in the company. What does it mean to you and your business?<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/au-blair-orange.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3>michel-noel<\/h3>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/robin-tabbers-teal.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3>Alan-Ang-teal<\/h3>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/betty.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3>ingi-ta<\/h3>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/expertise.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h4>Seamless regional service<\/h4>\n<div>\n<p>In Acclime&#8217;s obstacle-free structure, our partners have the drive and willingness to collaborate across borders irrespective of which of our offices will reap the benefit.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/attention.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h4>Hands-on attention<\/h4>\n<div>\n<p>Our clients receive far more hands-on attention from our senior managers and partners than they would at Big Four firms or similar corporate services providers in Asia.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/complications.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h4>Speed &#038; flexibility<\/h4>\n<div>\n<p>We are nimble, responsive and always able to help. Our partners can make swift and effective decisions on your behalf, cutting through bureaucracy and guiding you forward.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h6><span class=\"uk-icon uk-icon-image dot-alignment\" style=\"background-image: url(\/wp-content\/uploads\/dot.svg);\"><\/span> Brand values<\/h6>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<div>\n<h2>Our beliefs unlock true potential<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h2>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<h3>Expertise<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h3>\n<div>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0;\">Our local knowledge of complex Asian markets is unparalleled. But we get the big picture, too \u2014 with a global perspective that will help your business interests prosper.<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 12px;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/singapore.acclime.com\/case-studies\/conrad-maintenance\/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"el-link uk-button uk-button-text\" rel=\"noopener\">Read a relevant case study<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<h3>Agility<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h3>\n<div>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0;\">We help you navigate the most complex aspects of operating throughout Asia. Applying speed and dexterity to win you success, our reliability eases anxiety and stress in your operations.<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 12px;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/australia.acclime.com\/case-studies\/hawaiki\/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"el-link uk-button uk-button-text\" rel=\"noopener\">Read a relevant case study<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<h3>Innovation<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h3>\n<div>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0;\">Innovative thinking and new technology are what make Acclime different. Everything we do is geared to serve you and accelerate your business.<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 12px;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/hongkong.acclime.com\/case-studies\/carl-f-bucherer\/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"el-link uk-button uk-button-text\" rel=\"noopener\">Read a relevant case study<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<h3>Collaboration<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h3>\n<div>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0;\">Across Asian markets or in our own teams, working with you and for you, we believe combined efforts give the best outcome.<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 12px;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/china.acclime.com\/case-studies\/richard-wolf\/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"el-link uk-button uk-button-text\" rel=\"noopener\">Read a relevant case study<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<h3>Empathy<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h3>\n<div>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0;\">It\u2019s emotional intelligence that really sets us apart, thanks to deep roots country-by-country. Driving your business forward with fairness and humility.<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 12px;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/vietnam.acclime.com\/case-studies\/global-victoria\/\" class=\"el-link uk-button uk-button-text\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Read a relevant case study<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/mcrawford-1.png\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h2>Meet the people behind Acclime<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h2>\n<div>Get to know our team and find the right expert for you.<\/div>\n<p>\n    <a href=\"\/people\/\">Meet our people<\/a>\n<\/p>\n<p><!--more--><br \/>\n<!-- {\"children\":[{\"type\":\"section\",\"props\":{\"animation\":\"fade\",\"header_transparent\":\"light\",\"height\":\"full\",\"image_effect\":\"parallax\",\"image_height\":\"500\",\"image_parallax_bgx\":\"30,30\",\"imag